{
  "message": "test(conformance): add shape/stride metamorphic cases (+12)\n\nShape/stride metamorphic relations (12 cases):\n- reshape_flatten_roundtrip: reshape(flatten(x), shape) = x\n- transpose_transpose_identity: transpose(transpose(x)) = x\n- broadcast_scalar_idempotent: broadcast to same shape is identity\n- broadcast_commutative: broadcast(a, b) shape = broadcast(b, a) shape\n- squeeze_expand_inverse: expand_dims(squeeze(x)) recovers x\n- ravel_reshape_equivalence: ravel = reshape(-1)\n- contiguous_stride_product: C-order stride[i] = prod(shape[i+1:]) * itemsize\n- fortran_stride_product: F-order stride[i] = prod(shape[:i]) * itemsize\n- newaxis_dimension_increment: adding axis increases ndim by 1\n- broadcast_associative: broadcast(broadcast(a,b),c) = broadcast(a,broadcast(b,c))\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
